+[<807d5cf4>] (__napi_poll) from [<807d5f28>] (net_rx_action+0xf0/0x280)
+[<807d5f28>] (net_rx_action) from [<80302148>] (__do_softirq+0xd0/0x280)
+[<80302148>] (__do_softirq) from [<80320408>] (irq_exit+0x74/0xd4)
